60
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:28,460
ichi, ni, Sunshine

61
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:32,630
එකක්, දෙකක්, සන්ෂයින්

62
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:32,630
ichi, ni, Sunshine

63
